ccess controls, or mass scrape sites in violation of their terms of service. Abuse results in account termination without refund."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"7. Disclaimers"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The service is provided \"as is\" without warranty of any kind. Ashlar AI is not liable for indirect or consequential damages."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"8. Changes"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We may update these terms with at least 30 days' notice to active customers."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Contact"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"legal@getwebfetch.com"}]]}],null,["$","$L11",null,{"children":["$L12",["$","$L13",null,{"promise":"$@14"}]]}]]}]
